     H            Y.
      ** UTLR81B *********************************************
      *  UTILITY- ENTER EMAIL ADDRESS IF USER NOT FOUND      *
      *  LEC      2024.09.12                                 *
      *---------------------------------
      *  CALLING SEQ.
      *                    CALL 'UTLR81B'
      *                    PARM           $EMAIL 30
      *                    PARM           $RTN    1
      *  OUT $EMAIL: 30A EMAIL ADDRESS OF USER
      *      $RTN  :  1A RETURN CODE (BLANK/*)
      ********************************************************
     FUTLPW81 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FRGAPP01 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
      *
     E                    ERR     1   4 60
      *
      *
      * SYSTEM TIME(6) + DATE(6)
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WDTTM
     I                                        1   60WSTIME
     I                                        7  140WSDATE
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *-----------------------------------------------------------*
      *     M  A  I  N   R O U T I N E                            *
      *-----------------------------------------------------------*
     C                     EXSR #INIT
      *
     C           W@ID      DOWNE'99'
     C           W@ID      CASEQ'01'      @DSP1
     C                     ENDCS
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *************************************************************
      *  DISPLAY 1
      *************************************************************
     C           @DSP1     BEGSR
      *
     C                     EXFMTDSP01
     C                     MOVEL*BLANKS   XMSG
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN99
      * F1: CANCEL
     C           *INKA     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVEL'99'      W@ID
     C                     MOVE '*'       $RTN
     C                     GOTO @END1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     EXSR #CHK1
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVEL'99'      W@ID
     C                     MOVELXEMAIL    $EMAIL
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           @END1     ENDSR
      *************************************************************
      *  CHECK EMAIL ADDRESS
      *************************************************************
     C           #CHK1     BEGSR
      *
     C           XEMAIL    IFEQ *BLANKS
     C                     MOVELERR,1     XMSG
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     GOTO XCHK1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           XEMAIL    IFEQ ERR,2
     C                     MOVELERR,1     XMSG
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     GOTO XCHK1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     POS     40
     C           DOM       SCAN XEMAIL    POS
     C           POS       IFEQ *ZERO
     C                     MOVELERR,4     XMSG
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     GOTO XCHK1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * IF NO ERROR, UPDATE USER EMAIL ADDRESS FILE...
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     TIME           WDTTM
     C           #USER     CHAINRGAPP01              50
     C           *IN50     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVELXEMAIL    R1OGAD
     C                     MOVEL#USER     R1USER
     C                     Z-ADDWSDATE    R1KOHZ
     C                     Z-ADDWSTIME    R1KOJK
     C                     WRITERGAPP011
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVELXEMAIL    R1OGAD
     C                     Z-ADDWSDATE    R1KOHZ
     C                     Z-ADDWSTIME    R1KOJK
     C                     UPDATRGAPP011
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           XCHK1     ENDSR
      *************************************************************
      * INITIAL SET
      *************************************************************
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $EMAIL 30
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
     C           #USER     CHAINRGAPP01             N50
     C           *IN50     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVELR1OGAD    XEMAIL
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVELERR,2     XEMAIL
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $RTN
     C                     MOVEL'01'      W@ID    2
     C                     MOVELERR,3     DOM     9
      *
     C                     ENDSR
** (ERR) --------------------------------------------------> (60)
ENTER A VALID EMAIL ADDRESS
FIRST.LAST@IAFI.COM
@IAFI.COM
EMAIL ADDRESS SHOULD END WITH @IAFI.COM
